contentrichtext.text: '''XPT''' can mean multiple things: * The [[XPT (Train)|XPT passenger train]], a type of train operated by [[CountryLink]], the train and coach service that operates throughout regional areas in the state of [[New South Wales]], [[Australia]]. * The [[XPT (Extreme Power Tools)|XPT]], a Windows software toolset for programmers. * The [[ISO 4217]] code for tracking the value of one [[troy ounce]] of [[platinum]]. * The filename extension .xpt is used for [[XPConnect]] typelibraries. * The [[XPT Framework]] a web development [[Software framework|framework]] [[PHP]] based. * The [[XPT Garage door]] - a garage door brand. {{disambig}}
